---
// Substantive, human-readable body content for sport/hub pages.
// Gives search engines (Bing especially) real on-page text and a relevant
// internal-link graph instead of a single thin subtitle. Content is genuinely
// useful to a visitor: what's on, how to watch, what devices/languages work,
// and where to go next.
interface RelatedLink {
  href: string;
  label: string;
}

interface Props {
  /** Plain-language name of the sport/competition, e.g. "la NBA", "MotoGP". */
  subject: string;
  /** Short intro paragraph (1-2 sentences) describing what this page covers. */
  intro: string;
  /** Bullet-style highlights of what a visitor will find here. */
  highlights: string[];
  /** Optional extra context paragraph (schedule, season, teams, etc.). */
  context?: string;
  /** Related hub pages to link to internally. */
  related?: RelatedLink[];
}

const { subject, intro, highlights, context, related = [] } = Astro.props;
---
<section class="hub-content">
  <h2>Ver {subject} en vivo gratis</h2>
  <p>{intro}</p>

  {highlights.length > 0 && (
    <ul class="hub-highlights">
      {highlights.map((h) => <li>{h}</li>)}
    </ul>
  )}

  {context && <p>{context}</p>}

  <h3>¿Cómo ver {subject} en directo?</h3>
  <p>
    Abre el partido que quieras seguir, elige uno de los canales disponibles y el
    reproductor cargará la transmisión al instante. Si un canal va lento o no abre,
    selecciona otro: cada evento ofrece varias opciones en español, inglés y
    portugués. No necesitas registro ni instalar ninguna aplicación, y funciona
    desde el móvil, la tablet, el ordenador o la Smart TV.
  </p>

  {related.length > 0 && (
    <>
      <h3>Más deportes en vivo</h3>
      <p class="hub-related">
        {related.map((r, i) => (
          <>
            <a href={r.href}>{r.label}</a>{i < related.length - 1 ? ' · ' : ''}
          </>
        ))}
      </p>
    </>
  )}
</section>

<style>
  .hub-content {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 32px 0;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .hub-content h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .hub-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 24px 0 10px;
  }
  .hub-content p {
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .hub-highlights {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 4px 0 16px;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .hub-highlights li {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    padding: 4px 0 4px 22px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .hub-highlights li::before {
    content: '▸';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--red);
  }
  .hub-related a {
    color: var(--red) !important;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
